                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 13.547,
                                "byte_start": 91005,
                                "byte_stop": 145235,
                                "text": "The second case that I have to announce, Key Tronic Corporation against the United States, arises out of the dispute between two of the parties responsible for pollution of a landfill site in the State of Washington."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 13.547,
                                "stop": 19.317,
                                "byte_start": 145235,
                                "byte_stop": 168327,
                                "text": "Both Key Tronic and the United States Air force dump liquid chemicals in the landfill."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 19.317,
                                "stop": 31.339,
                                "byte_start": 168327,
                                "byte_stop": 216393,
                                "text": "In litigation with the Washington State Department of Ecology and the Federal Environmental Protection Agency, Key Tronic agreed to contribute over $4 million to the cost of cleaning up the site."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 31.339,
                                "stop": 40.949,
                                "byte_start": 216393,
                                "byte_stop": 254845,
                                "text": "In this action, Key Tronic seeks to recover a significant portion of those costs from the United States Air Force because it was also partially responsible for the pollution."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 40.949,
                                "stop": 49.341,
                                "byte_start": 254845,
                                "byte_stop": 288386,
                                "text": "The specific question we have to decide is whether in such an action one responsible party may recover its attorney\u0027s fees from another."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 49.341,
                                "stop": 73.476,
                                "byte_start": 288386,
                                "byte_stop": 384935,
                                "text": "The amount at issue is approximately $1.2 million for fees that covered three different types of services: First, the identification of other potentially responsible parties, including the Air Force, that was liable for the pollution; second, the preparation and negotiation of a settlement agreement with the EPA; and finally, that fees incurred in the prosecution of this litigation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 73.476,
                                "stop": 81.889,
                                "byte_start": 384935,
                                "byte_stop": 418581,
                                "text": "For reasons stated in an opinion filed with the Clerk, we hold that fees of the first of those three types of services are recoverable but the others are not."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 81.889,
                                "stop": 89.025,
                                "byte_start": 418581,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Justice Scalia has filed an opinion dissenting in part in which he has joined by Justice Blackmun and Justice Thomas."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
